Entry.Name: SHOUTStarcraft
Entry.Description: SHOUTcraft is a weekly event hosting all-platinum games with commentator TotalBiscuit, winner of Blizzard's Shoutcasting contest 2009 and occassional guest commentators. He presents in a format that's appealing to new players and those not into the eSports scene and intend to act as a gateway to other more advanced commentators such as Day[9]. You can expect high-octane commentary in the style of a sports broadcast, think professional wrestling or boxing, avoiding the technical jargon in favour of the exciting and the dramatic.
